headline: Wall Street Analysts See VICI Properties (VICI) as a Buy: Should You Invest?
summary: Based on the average brokerage recommendation (ABR), VICI Properties (VICI) should be added to one's portfolio. Wall Street analysts' overly optimistic recommendations cast doubt on the effectiveness of this highly sought-after metric. So, is the stock worth buying?
